sketch.compiler.ast.core

Class Parameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.Parameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Parameter>

    public class Parameter
extends FENode
implements java.lang.Comparable<Parameter>
    A formal parameter to a function. Each parameter consists of a string name, a Type, and a integer Ptype which indicates wether the parameter is input-only, output-only, or both.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
